summary: This document outlines the cost reimbursement rates for various types of records services provided by T-Mobile, including call detail records, wiretap services, and customer care memos. It includes pricing for both real-time and archived records, as well as contact information for legal inquiries.
keyFacts: The document provides a detailed rate schedule for T-Mobile's records services.
Rates include $5800 for certain order renewals and $30 per target per day for real-time services.
There is a $50 service fee for archived records requests.
Contact information for legal inquiries is provided, including specific email addresses for different types of questions.
The information is protected from disclosure under U.S. law.
